</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[499,555,1935,1958]" pageId="14" pageNumber="61" rank="species">n. sp.</taxonomicNameLabel>
a hypopygium, left lateral. b. male postabdomen with phallus extended, left lateral; c. male tarsus I, posterior view. d. male wing, dorsal. 
<taxonomicName box="[735,886,1972,1995]" class="Insecta" family="Dolichopodidae" genus="Mesorhaga" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="61" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="baadsvicki" status="n. sp.">
<emphasis box="[735,886,1972,1995]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="61">
M. 
